highlights.text: Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Patna the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Patna. Kesariya is the highest at #4.
Ram Siya Ram by Sachet Tandon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Patna, up 63 spots at #36.
Ajab Si (From "Om Shanti Om") by KK is the highest new entry on Top Songs Patna at #67.
